text.tspan: "If I keep smoking at this rate, my smoking can cause cancer."
"My colleagues don't approve or disapprove of my smoking."
"I am ashamed of being a smoker."
"For me, smoking is something I do automatically."
"I am not confident I can successfully quit smoking in the next month."
"I am able to decline cigarettes even when I experience craving."
"Smoking helps me to make contact with people in bars."
"Smoking helps me relax when I feel stressed."
"For me, it is too late to quit anyway."
"I do not think smoking is a disgusting habit."
It is never too late to quit.
Your colleagues expect you to quit smoking.
Role model saying "I was ashamed of being a smoker."
Craving usually lasts only a few minutes.
